headline: Blackstone Strategic Partners Closes Largest Infrastructure Secondaries Fund Ever Raised at $5.5 Billion
summary: NEW YORK, September 02, 2025--Blackstone (NYSE:BX) announced the final close on $5.5 billion for its latest infrastructure secondaries fund, Strategic Partners Infrastructure IV L.P., and its related committed program vehicles. SP Infrastructure IV is the world’s largest dedicated infrastructure secondaries fund raised to-date.
